		<div class="container smrt-content-container">
		<div class="smrt-content row">
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-10 col-md-push-1 col-xl-8 col-xl-push-2">
				<h1>Welcome Opera Suites Vienna</h1>
			</div>
			
						<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-10 col-md-push-1 col-xl-8 col-xl-push-2 text-center">
				<h4>
	Bed &amp; Breakfast in the City Centre of Vienna&nbsp;</h4>
<p>We welcome you <a href="/en/bed-and-breakfast-near-opera-house-vienna/">in the heart of Vienna</a> with personal service and charming hospitality, around the corner from the famous Vienna State Opera House at K&auml;rntner Strasse. Our House combines the <a href="/en/bed-and-breakfast-near-opera-house-vienna/">best location with Viennese charm</a>. Opera lovers, Vienna tourists and business travellers will feel right at home in the <a href="/en/apartments-vienna-city-centre/">comfortable rooms</a> of our hotel and well looked after by our friendly personal service.</p>
<p>The 12 rooms of our family run Bed &amp; Breakfast are located on the first and second floor of a historical Viennese Town House from the turn of the century. All <a href="/en/apartments-vienna-city-centre/">our rooms</a> are furnished and decorated with great attention to detail in Viennese style and offer our guests modern comfort and amenities.</p>
<p><em><strong>Our reception is open daily from 7 am to 8 pm. If you are arriving after 8 pm, please let us know in advance.</strong></em></p>
<p><em><strong><a href="http://www.citypension.at/index_en.html" title="City PENSION">Visit also our partner company City PENSION</a></strong></em></p>
			</div>
											</div>
			</div>
	
